e": "08:17", "author": "TankerTrackers", "author_name": "TankerTrackers.com, Inc.", "followers": 227035, "views": 72853, "likes": 467, "replies": 27, "retweets": 127, "quotes": 27, "bookmarks": 57, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067895277818638734", "url": "https://x.com/FluxOfficials/status/2067895277818638734", "text": "KPC announces rescinding Force Majeure and resumption of production thanks to MoU and improving market conditions \n#OOTT #Oil #OilPrices https://t.co/F2303k6RKl", "time": "09:00", "author": "FluxOfficials", "author_name": "The Officials", "followers": 1859, "views": 941, "likes": 6, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2067952745773142491", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067952745773142491", "text": "Here is the administrative requirements to get through the straits of Hormuz \n\nEven when open to all, Iran decides who can pass and when.   \n\nDon’t think of Hormuz as open or closed.    Think of it like a tap that can be open anywhere from a dribble to a jet.   #oott", "time": "12:48", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 1191, "likes": 9, "replies": 4, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2067952923108118844", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067952923108118844", "text": "Iran is requiring all vessels that want to pass the strait to fill in a form on: https://t.co/zHUFxI6rau and gain permission prior to passage #OOTT", "time": "12:49", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 82711, "likes": 163, "replies": 13, "retweets": 39, "quotes": 12, "bookmarks": 20, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067953678510604302", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067953678510604302", "text": "Senior US Official: Israel, Hezbollah Have Agreed To A Ceasefire At 16:00 Local Time On Friday\n\n#OOTT", "time": "12:52", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 12882, "likes": 34, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2067955710353113545", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067955710353113545", "text": "A senior American official tells me: Israel and Hezbollah have agreed to a renewed ceasefire starting at 16:00 Israel time. The new agreement was reached through US and Qatar mediation after talks with Israel and Iran.\n\n#OOTT", "time": "13:00", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 9775, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2067966334210805872", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067966334210805872", "text": "Think of the odds of Israel leaving Lebanon as equal to the Straits of Hormuz staying open.\n\nThen place time limits on that equation, 1 day, 5 day, 10 day, 30 day, 60 day to establish probabilities.\n\nThen match those with the probabilities of tank bottoms in 30, 60, 90 days #OOTT", "time": "13:42", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 2233, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2067973752101433724", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067973752101433724", "text": "Iran Rejects Claims On Closure Of Strait Of Hormuz – Foreign Ministry\n\n#OOTT", "time": "14:12", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 9323, "likes": 19, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067974459990880680", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2067974459990880680", "text": "MAP OF THE DAY: Iran has published a new chart showing two shipping lanes in Hormuz to the south of the ones that Tehran unveiled weeks ago. The new lanes are to the north of the ones used before the war. The Omani lane remains in operation too. \n\nBefore (left) and now (right) https://t.co/oDIVgmolg", "time": "14:15", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 41255, "likes": 270, "replies": 17, "retweets": 81, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 61, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067974870558785543", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067974870558785543", "text": "Pakistan Reports Mine in Strait of Hormuz Area\n#oott", "time": "14:16", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 66495, "likes": 92, "replies": 4, "retweets": 20, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2067999006882508885", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067999006882508885", "text": "#OOTT | US Intelligence Warns Israel Is Likely To Undermine Iran Peace Deal, Officials Say – @washingtonpost \nhttps://t.co/5aMO9ziniJ", "time": "15:52", "author"